OL,3,C'Amazing' school trip could become
OL,4,Ccompulsory but not everyone agrees
OL,6,FThere are calls for all school
OL,7,Fchildren in Wales to receive a week of
OL,8,Fresidential outdoor education, funded
OL,9,Fby the
OL,11,FSenedd members will vote next month on
OL,12,Fa bill which would see each child take
OL,13,Fpart in a compulsory week away from
OL,14,Fhome. Supporters of the bill claim it
OL,15,Fwill give young people a valuable
OL,16,Ffirst taste of independence and
OL,17,Fimprove their wellbeing.
