OL,3,C'Amazing' school trip could become
OL,4,Ccompulsory but not everyone agrees
OL,6,FAndy Meek, who runs the Storey Arms
OL,7,FOutdoor Education Centre near Pen y
OL,8,FFan, told : "I'm supporting this bill
OL,9,Fbecause I think it's crucial to our
OL,10,Fyoung people's education.
OL,12,F"I've been involved in this world for
OL,13,F40 years and I know the value of it to
OL,14,Fthe young people that come and visit."
OL,16,FStorey Arms is located in the heart of
OL,17,Fthe and offers visitors the chance to
OL,18,Ftake part in activities like hiking,
OL,19,Fcanoeing, caving and gorge walking.
