OL,3,C'Amazing' school trip could become
OL,4,Ccompulsory but not everyone agrees
OL,6,FIt is one of a number of centres
OL,7,Facross the country which offer young
OL,8,Fpeople this kind of experience.
OL,10,FMr Meek added: "Many schools come but
OL,11,Fit's only accessible to the ones who
OL,12,Fcan afford to pay and come to a centre
OL,13,Flike this. It would be so good if we
OL,14,Fknew we could open access to everybody
OL,15,Fto come and that would just help the
OL,16,Fpeople who don't have the chance to
OL,17,Fexperience such an amazing time away
OL,18,Ffrom home."
